## Limitations
The primary limitation of this report is the reliance on secondary sources, which may not provide a comprehensive view of the historical context of gender inequality. Additionally, the lack of specific dates and detailed historical data in some sources limits the ability to pinpoint the exact origins and evolution of gender inequality. Further research, including archaeological and anthropological studies, would be beneficial to gain a more nuanced understanding of this complex issue.